<title depth="1">4<tab/>Requirements</title>
<p id="_68e1e8e1-2a9e-84f7-806f-7dfffdaf4735">Basic requirements for running Metanorma systems are as follows.</p>

<clause id="_system_setup" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">
<title depth="2">4.1<tab/>System Setup</title>
<p id="_e7644ba7-b2fd-642e-ced4-4b7d2d11a77f">Docker Desktop must be installed on your host machine.</p>
</clause>

<clause id="_image_verification" inline-header="false" obligation="normative">
<title depth="2">4.2<tab/>Image Verification</title>
<p id="_5d0f0baf-3454-0157-d922-26f709ffcdc2">The Metanorma docker image must be successfully pulled.</p>
</clause>
</clause>




